{"word":"ἐμός","slug":"ἐμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐμός, ή, όν</el></b> [via <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐμέ\">ἐμέ</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> possessive <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pron.\">pron.</a> of 1 <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> <b>my, mine <a href='B:470 18:20'>Mt 18:20</a>; <a href='B:480 8:38'>Mk 8:38</a>; <a href='B:500 3:29'>J 3:29</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in J; <b><a href='B:520 3:7'>Ro 3:7</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Paul; <b><a href='B:680 1:15'>2 Pt 1:15</a>; <a href='B:710 1:1'>3 J 4</a>; <a href='B:730 2:20'>Rv 2:20</a>.—</b>With emphasis τῇ ἐμῇ χειρί with my own hand <b><a href='B:530 16:21'>1 Cor 16:21</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <b>—</b>In place of the objective <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> τὴν ἐμὴν ἀνάμνησιν</el> in memory of me <b><a href='B:490 22:19'>Lk 22:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as noun <el>τὸ ἐμόν</el> my property <b><a href='B:470 25:27'>Mt 25:27</a></b> (here <el>τὸ ἐ.</el> = my money); <el>τὰ ἐμά</el> what belongs to me <b><a href='B:470 20:15'>Mt 20:15</a>; <a href='B:490 15:31'>Lk 15:31</a>; <a href='B:500 17:10'>J 17:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐμοί\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐμπαιγμονή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}